{"tid":1748173,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔投票或投白票都係出賣兄弟","createTime":"2019-11-23T14:07:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T14:40:26.000Z","uid":264958,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a2a9b0eae7e6876a0103ef1f560e713b7c1c76db","tid":1748173,"uid":264958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T14:07:41.000Z","msg":"之後寫過一次，希望出多次post <br />\n拉得一個得一個<br />\n<br />\n我地今次真係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔輸得</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔投票、投白票<br />\n都係出賣香港人<br />\n出賣手足<br />\n<br />\n唔投泛民，會放番一堆民賤聯工聯會入區議會<br />\n<br />\n唔投泛民，到時建制派大勝，連國際輿論都輸埋<br />\n<br />\n輸左之後，對家可以日日大字標題話證明民意支持政府止暴制亂<br />\n<br />\n泛民係廢，但當初無佢地喺立法會阻止法案委員會選主席，就無之後嘅事<br />\n<br />\n民主黨係入過中聯辦，但已經十九幾年前，呢一代白鴿呢場運動真係出過力<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打贏場區選對我哋唔會有害，點解唔做？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">星期日<br />\n香港需要你一票</span></span>"},{"pid":"a4f7cbd0ed084faeb1580e42788720e4ec867496","tid":1748173,"uid":264958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T14:09:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9PBbGEo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9PBbGEo.jpg&h=6cfcd64d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5699feae51d55f8c2b9f947a6f267ad851283f11","tid":1748173,"uid":326017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T14:09:16.000Z","msg":"所羅門講到明 今次係民主/共產主義之爭<br />\n白票撚姐係共產主義支持者 支持佢地返大灣區"},{"pid":"0261483be12f1ae667e073d431956b17767a58b8","tid":1748173,"uid":264958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T14:09:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MxKsZq9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMxKsZq9.jpg&h=b65732d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5383ddeaebc916858d432421d1db56f522e74b2a","tid":1748173,"uid":264958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T14:10:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UusRGED.jpg\" data-th